snippet.textDisplay: I don't really comment on Coke studio because I am not a music critic but That was Disappointing! I tried my best to like it. Meesha Shafi is overrated and Naeem Abbas was just wasted. The music arrangement was out of place, Shuja trying too many things at the same time and coming up with some 90s bollywoodish DDLJ style shadi song. Its just my opinion nobody has to agree with this, but I hope he reads it someday and realize that he just overused his potential in coke studio.
